content: tell me about the qualifications of shyam sundar

Shyam Sundar is an individual with technical skills in Python, C/C++, SQL, and various frameworks and tools. He has completed an M.Tech in Modelling and Simulation and a B.Tech in Chemical Engineering. Shyam Sundar has worked on projects like LLM-Powered Coupon Recommender and PeopleCare Insurance Prediction.
